Kim-ku3: Li2 m7-thang him-soan7 phainn2-lang5, tok8-tok8 tioh8 thong-jit8 keng3-ui3 Ia5-ho5-hoa. (Chim-gian5 23:17)
Bok8-tek: Sou2-lo5-bun5 ong5 ni5-lau7 e5 si5, tui3 i koe3-khi3 sou2 keng-giam7, chai se3-kan e5 khang-hi, jin7-bat chi2-u7 keng3-ui3 Siong7-te3, chun-than3 I e5 beng7-leng7 chiah u7 hok-khi3.
Lan2 tioh8 ka3-si7 hak8-seng hou7 in beng5-pek8, tioh8 ti7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok tui-kiu5 chiah e5 chin-li2, chin e5 hok-khi3.
Sio2 peng5-iu2, lin2 bat khoann3 lang5 teh hip-siong7 bo5? Chin sim-sek hounn3? Chhiak! Chit8-tiunn lah...... se3-kai3 che7-che7 chiau3-siong3-ki e5 tiong-kan, Kho-lat-khuh e5 chiau3-siong3-ki chin chhut-mia5. Cha2-khi2 beh kong2 hit e5 thau5-ke e5 kou3-su7. I ti7 se3-kai3 e5 mui2 chit8 sou2-chai7 long2 u7 i e5 hun-tiam3. Se poann3-kiu5 e5 tiam3 khui-mng5 cho3 seng-li2, Tang poann3-kiu5 e5 tiam3 koainn-mng5 teh khun3; Tang poann3-kiu5 khui-mng5 cho3 seng-li2, Se poann3-kiu5 koainn-mng5 teh khun3, thang kong2 me5-jit8 long2 teh cho3 seng-li2.
Bi2-kok mui2 chit8-keng toa7 e5 gun5-hang5 long2 u7 i e5 chun5-khoann2, i thang sui5-i3 khui chi-phio3 nia2-chinn5. I e5 than3-chinn5 m7-si7 eng7 1 ni5 a2-si7 1 goeh8-jit8 si7 eng7 mui2 bio2 lai5 ke3-sng3. I thang chiau3 ka-ki7 sou2 ai3, hiong2-siu7 it-chhe3 e5 hok-lok8. I tak8-hang7 long2 chiau5-pi7, kho2-sioh khiam3 chit8-hang7, chiu7-si7 bo5 Siong7-te3; bo5 Siong7-te3 chiu7 bo5 peng5-an. Pat8-lang5 khoann3 i si7 hok-khi3, khoai3-lok8 e5 lang5, chong2-si7 i pun2-sin si7 chap8-hun e5 thong3-khou2. Lai7-sim e5 thong3-khou2, pi2 jiok8-the2 e5 thong3-khou2 khah siong-tiong7. I m7-chai tioh8 chainn2-iunn7 cho3 chiah oe7 ho2. Se3-kan lang5 sou2 eng7 e5 hong-hoat, i long2 i2-keng cho3 liau2, u7 chinn5 u7 se3, sim2-mih8 cho3 boe7 kau3?
Chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 peng5-an m7-si7 eng7 chinn5 u7 tang3 be2 e5! Sou2-i2 koh-khah kan-khou2, choe3-au7 i siunn7 beh seh8 se3-kai3, iu5 se3-kai3 khoann3 ti7 se3-kai3 e5 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7 thang hou7 i tit-tioh8 chin e5 peng5-an, kai2-koat i e5 khou2-thang3? I chhoe7 peng5-an, chong2-si7 bo5-ai3 Siong7-te3, kiat-ko2 se3-kai3 i2-keng iu5 liau2 lah, khou2-bun7 koh-khah chhim-tang7, kau3-boe2 tui3 choat8-bang7 lai5 hoe5-sim, tui3 hoe5-sim lai5 siunn7 kiann5 te2-pou7, choe3-au7 beh tng2-khi3 Bi2-kok e5 lou7-tiong thiau3-hai2 chu7-sat!
Sio2 peng5-iu2, chit e5 ho2-giah8 lang5 hiah-nih8 ho2-giah8, kau3-boe2 tit-tioh8 sim2-mih8? Siann2-su7 oe7 an2-ni? (Bo5 Siong7-te3) Si7 chin gau5. Na7 bo5 Siong7-te3, boe7-hiau2 keng3-ui3 Siong7-te3 e5 lang5 si7 chin kho2-lin5.
Kou2-cha2 Sou2-lo5-bun5 ong5, i cho3 ong5, u7 chinn5 u7 se3, koh u7 hak8-bun7, chong2-si7 i ia7 bat keng-giam7 tioh8 chhin-chhiunn7 Kho-lat-khuh e5 thau5-ke e5 kan-khou2, chong2-si7 kai-chai3 i choe3-au7 u7 chhoe7 tioh8 Siong7-te3, oe7-hiau2 keng3-ui3 Siong7-te3 chiah bo5 kiann5 chu7-sat e5 lou7. Au7-lai5 i u7 sia2 i e5 keng-giam7 lai5 ka3-si7 lan2. Kin-a2-jit8 e5 kim-ku3 ia7-si7 i sou2 sia2--e5. Lan2 koh sann-kap lai5 liam7: “Li2 m7-thang him-soan7 phainn2-lang5, tok8-tok8 tioh8 thong-jit8 keng3-ui3 Ia5-ho5-hoa.” (Chim-gian5 23:17)
Lan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou kong2: “Lang5 na7 tit-tioh8 choan5 se3-kai3, lai5 song3-sit i e5 sinn3-mia7 u7 sim2-mih8 li7-ek?” (Ma2-thai3 16:26). Sio2 peng5-iu2, lin2 ai3 choan5 se3-kai3 a2-si7 sinn3-mia7? (sinn3-mia7), chin gau5, lan2 na7 beh tit sinn3-mia7 tioh8 siong5-siong5 keng3-pai3 Siong7-te3, thiann Chu2 e5 ka3-si7, kiann5 Chu2 sou2 ka3-si7 lan2 e5 lou7, an2-ni chiu7 oe7-thang tit eng2-oan2 e5 sinn3-mia7. (T. H. C.)
