Kim-ku3: Goan2 bo5 ti3-kau3 biat8-bo5, si7 tui3 Ia5-ho5-hoa chiah e5 chu5-ai3. (Ai-ko 3:22)
Ti7 chia kong2 3 e5 soan-kau3-su e5 kou3-su7, in ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 kang-chok tit-tioh8 I e5 thiann3-thang3 m7-na7 ka-ki7 bo5 sit-loh8 sinn3-mia7, hoan2-tng2 tui3 i lai5 kiu3 loa7 che7 e5 leng5-hun5 bo5 biat8-bo5.
1. Ti7 chit8-pah goa7 ni5-cheng5 tui3 Sou-kek-lan5 u7 chit8-ui7 soan-kau3-su, chi3-goan7 kau3 Lam5-iunn5 e5 to2-su7 u7 che7-che7 chiah8 lang5-bah e5 thou2-lang5 e5 sou2-chai7 thoan5 hok-im, u7 chit8-pai2 chiah e5 thou2-lang5 beh thai5 i chiu7 pang3-hoe2 sio i e5 chhu3, chit e5 soan-kau3-su ti7 chhu3-lai7 chi2-u7 kui7 teh ki5-to2, hut-jian5-kan hong chin thau3, hoe2 soa3 poe tui3 thou2-lang5 e5 chhu3, soan-kau3-su e5 chhu3 bo5 sio khi3 sinn3-mia7 tit-tioh8 kiu3, koh u7 chit8-pai2 hou7 thou2-lang5 tui kau3 chau2 bo5 lou7, kau3 chit8 e5 kia7-teng2 koh khi3 chiu7 bo5 lou7 e5 si5, i chiu7 thiau3 loh8-khi3 kui2-na7 tng7 chhim e5 sou2-chai7, in-ui7 u7 gia5 chit8-ki hou7-soann3 thi2-khui i long2 bo5 tioh8-siong.
2. Ti7 chit8-pah goa7 ni5-cheng5, Eng-kok chit8-ui7 i-seng chi3-goan7 beh khi3 A-hui-li7-ka thoan5 to7-li2, i ti7 Eng-kok e5 si5 kha hou7 chhia kauh-tng7-khi3, au7-lai5 eng7 chin iong2 e5 chhiu7-leng choe3 chit8-ki ke2 e5 kha tau3 ti7 kha-thui2, i kau3 A-hui-li7-ka, hou7 chiah8 lang5-bah e5 thou2-lang5 liah8-khi3, beh oah8-thai5 lai5 chiah8 i e5 bah, i chiu7 kong2, Goa2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 lang5, goa2 e5 bah lin2 na7 kann2 chiah8, to theh8 lai5 goa2 koah chit8-te3 hou7 lin2 chiah8, soan-kau3-su tit-tioh8 to chiu7 koah hit e5 chhiu7-leng ke2-kha e5 chhiu7-leng chit8-te3 hou7 thou2-lang5-thau5, thou2-lang5 ka7 hit-te3 bah e5 si5 chhui3-khi2 hiam2 tng7-khi3, chiu7 kong2, Lin2 Siong7-te3 e5 lang5-bah chin thang kiann. Au7-lai5 soan-kau3-su ti7 hia thoan5-to7 chiann5-choe3 A-hui-li7-ka e5 kng-chhenn.
3. Ti7 80 goa7 ni5-cheng5 Eng-kok chit8-ui7 soan-kau3-su lai5 Tai5-oan5 thoan5 to7-li2, u7 chit8-pai2 kau3 Koan-a2-nia2 hu7-kin7 Peh8-chui2-khe e5 hiunn-sia7 thoan5 to7-li2 tu2-tioh8 thou2-hui2, u7 chit8-mi5 thou2-hui2 beh thai5--i, chiu7 pang3-hoe2 sio soan-kau3-su sou2 toa3 hit keng chhu3, si3-ui5 long2 chin iam7 e5 hoe2 sit8-chai7 choat8-bang7, chong2-si7 soan-kau3-su kui7 teh ki5-to2, Siong7-te3 chiu7 khui ti3-hui7 hou7 i, i chiu7 chiong mi5-chioh-phoe7 kng2-kng2 leh, tui3 toa7-mng5 khui chiu7 hiat chhut-khi3, thou2-hui2 liah8-chun2 soan-kau3-su chau2 chhut-lai5, chiu7 tit8-tit8 ka7 i kong3, tng hiah e5 thou2-hui2 chu7-chip8 teh kong3 mi5-chioh-phoe7 e5 si5, soan-kau3-su tui3 au7-boe2-mng5 chau2 chhut-khi3 loh8 soann kau3 Ka-gi7 an2-ni kiu3 tioh8 mia7.
Seng3-keng kong2, Siong7-te3 na7 ui7 lan2 chi7-chui7 beh ti2-tek8 lan2, lan2 na7 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 thiann3 e5, chiu7 tui3 I e5 chu5-ai3 tek-khak bo5 ti3-kau3 biat8-bo5. (I. L. Chhi5)
