Kim-ku3: Kinn3-na7 ho2 e5 siunn2-su3, kap oan5-choan5 e5 un-su3, long2 si7 tui3 teng2-bin7. (Nga2-kok 1:17)
Kok-ui7 sio2 peng5-iu2 lin2 tak8-jit8 sou2 chheng7 u7 sui2 e5 sann, sou2 chiah8 e5 png7 kap ho2 chiah8-mih8, lin2 e5 chinn5, lin2 sou2 thak8 e5 chheh si7 chi7-chui7 hou7 lin2 e5? Si7, si7 lin2 pa-pa ma-ma siunn2-su3 lin2 e5. In tak8-jit8 ui7-tioh8 lin2 lai5 bo5-eng5 kap siu7 chin choe7 e5 kan-khou2, eng7 sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 oan5-choan5 peh8-peh8 siunn2-su3 lin2, sit8-chai7 chin thiann3 lin2, ti7 chit se3-kai3 kiam2-chhai2 si7 pa-pa ma-ma choe3 thiann3 li2, chong2-si7 ti7 thinn-teng2 u7 chit8-ui7 koh-khah thiann3 li2 e5 Siong7-te3.
I tak8-jit8 long2 teh chiau3-kou3 li2, sui-jian5 li2 bo5 khoann3-tioh8 I chong2-si7 I long2 tiam3 ti7 li2 e5 sin-pinn teh po2-hou7 li2, li2 na7 u7 sim2-mih8 khiam3-khoeh I long2 e7 siunn2-su3 lin2, u7-si5 li2 khiam3 e5 mih8 li2 e5 pa-pa ma-ma m7-chai, tioh8 li2 tui3 in tho2 chiah oe7 hou7 li2, chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 chiu7 m7-si7 an2-ni, I oe7 khoann3-chhut li2 e5 sim, chai-iann2 li2 sou2 khiam3-khoeh e5, I tai7-seng ka7 li2 pi7-pan7 pian7-pian7. I sou2 siunn2-su3 e5 pi2 li2 e5 pa-pa ma-ma ke chin choe7, I ia7 oe7 siunn2-su3 ti3-hui7, che si7 lang5 choe3 boe7 kau3 e5, sou2-i2 tu2-tioh8 sou2 liam7 e5 hit e5 kim-ku3 kong2: “Kinn3-na7 ho2 e5 siunn2-su3 kap oan5-choan5 e5 un-su3, long2 si7 tui3 teng2-bin7 lai5 e5.”
Ti7 si3-chheng goa7 ni5-cheng5 Tiong-kok u7 chit8 e5 hong5-te3 mia5 kio3 Sun3. I m7-na7 si7 chit8 e5 chin ho2 e5 hong5-te3, ia7-si7 chit8 e5 chin iu2-hau3 e5 lang5, sou2-i2 lang5-lang5 long2 o-lo2 i, chun-keng3 i.
I si7 chhut-si3 ti7 chit8 e5 san3-hiong e5 choh-sit e5 ka-teng5, I e5 lau7-pe7 mia7 kio3 Kou2-sou2, si7 chit8 e5 m7-bat se3-su7, chin bo5 beng5-pek8 e5 lang5, lang5 na7 kong2 an2-choann2-iunn7, i tioh8 chiau3 an2-ni sin3, chiau3 an2-ni cho3, Sun3 e5 sinn-bo2 ti7 i se3-han3 e5 si5 chiu7 si2, i e5 au7-bo2 si7 chit8 e5 gong7 koh phainn2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, au7-bo2 sinn chit8 e5 sio2-ti7 mia5 kio3-choe3 Chhiunn7, ia7-si7 chit8 e5 chin phainn2 e5 gin2-na2.
Au7-bu2 e5 sim chin tok8, thiann3 i ka-ki7 sou2 sinn e5, oan3-hun7 Sun3, siong5-siong5 phainn2 khoan2-thai7 i, i e5 lau7-pe7 in-ui7 thiann au7-bu2 e5 oe7, ia7 chin thiann3 i e5 sio2-ti7, oan3-hun7 i, lian5 i e5 sio2-ti7 in-ui7 siunn7 pa-pa ma-ma long2 khah thiann3 i, sou2-i2 siong5-siong5 ti7 pe7-bu2 e5 bin7-cheng5 lai5 kong2 hiann-ko e5 m7-ho2, lai5 me7 i, khi-hu7 i, au7-bu2 ia7 siong5-siong5 ti7 i e5 lau7-pe7 e5 bin7-cheng5 kong2 i e5 phainn2-oe7, chong2-si7 bo5-lun7 lang5 tui3 i chainn2-iunn7 phainn2, i long2 bo5 ke3-kau3, ia7 bo5 siu7-khi3, ia7-si7 chin hau3-keng3 i e5 pe7-bu2, ia7 chin thiann3 i e5 sio2-ti7.
In ju2 phainn2 khoan2-thai7 i, i ju2 hau3-keng3, u7 chit8-pai2 siu7 koann2 chhut-khi3, li7-khui ka-teng5 kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7 khi3 phiau-liu5, cho3 tak8-khoan2 e5 khou2-kang, chong2-si7 i ia7 long2 bo5 chit8-ku3 e5 oan3-gian5, hoan2-tng2 koh-khah thiann3 i e5 pe7-bu2 kap sio2-ti7.
Sio2 peng5-iu2, li2 oe7 oh8 i boe7? Na7 u7 pat8-lang5 tui3 li2 phainn2 li2 beh kap i phainn2 a2-si7 beh chhiunn7 Sun3 koh-khah thiann3 i? Sun3 sui-jian5 an2-ni tui3-thai7 in chong2-si7 chan5-jim2 e5 pe7-bu2 kap khiau-ngou7 e5 sio2-ti7 ia7 bo5 siu7 kam2-tong7, hoan2-tng2 ju2 phainn2 khoan2-thai7 i, u7-si5 siunn7 ai3 beh ka7 i hai7-si2. U7 chit8-pai2 kio3 i khi3 siu-li2 chhu3-teng2, tng i chiunn7 chhu3-teng2 e5 si5, i e5 sio2-ti7 chiong thui gia5 chau2 jian5-au7 tui3 e7-bin7 pang3-hoe2 sio-chhu3, ai3 beh ka7 i sio si2, kai-chai3 i u7 chun2-pi7 nng7-teng2 “koe-leh8”, tng hoe2 sio kau3 chhu3-teng2 e5 si5, i chiu7 kiap hit nng7-teng2 koe-leh8 thiau3 loh8-lai5, bian2-tit ti3-kau3 si2.
Au7-lai5 koh u7 chit8-pai2 i e5 pa-pa kio3 i loh8-khi3 chit8 e5 kou2-chinn2 beh ou2 khah chhim leh, tng i loh8-khi3 e5 si5, i e5 sio2-ti7 tui3 bin7-teng2 eng7 chioh8-thau5 kap thou5 chiong chit e5 chinn2 thun7 khi2-lai5, beh chiong i oah8-oah8 tai5 si2, chit pai2 i e5 sio2-ti7 sim-lai7 chin-chiann3 hoann-hi2, liah8-choe3 i it-teng7 chau2 boe7 chhut-lai5 si2 ti7 chinn2 lai7 lah, chiu7 chin hoann-hi2 khi3 tui3 i e5 pe7-bu2 kong2, “Hiann-ko e5 gu5-iunn5, chinn5 kap i e5 chai5-san2 kap it-chhe3 sou2 u7 e5 long2 siok8 ti7 goa2 e5 lah.”
